2026-05-12T04:14:11.1707837Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-12T04:14:11.1708727Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T04:14:11.1709559Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T04:14:11.1710423Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T04:14:11.1711281Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T04:14:11.1712125Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
